，整形常数默认是int，浮点型常数默认是double。 自动类型提升基本数据类型转换的规则如下（byte、short、char是平级）： 存储范围小的数据类型的值赋值给存储范围大的数据类型的变量 12int i = &#x27;a&#x27;; // char自动升级为intdouble d = 100; // int自动升级为double","categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://komorecoi.github.io/categories/Java/"}],"tags":[]}],"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://komorecoi.github.io/categories/Java/"}],"tags":[{"name":"集合","slug":"集合","permalink":"https://komorecoi.github.io/tags/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/"}]}